title: Wrap around Patios/ Large Laundry Rooms!!
posting_body: THIS IS A MASTER PLANNED LUXURTY COMMUNITY.
THEY OFFER SEVERAL DIFFERENT FLOOR PLANS.
THERE IS ONE TO MEET YOUR NEEDS.
SUPPLIED WASHER AND DRYERS IN ALL UNITS.
SOME UNITS INCLUDE A DEN AREA, AND ATTACHED GARAGES.
THE PROPERTY IS ON A COMPERIZED PRICING SYSTEM THAT CHANGES EVERY THREE DAYS, THE PRICES ARE BASED ON AVAILABILITY.
THE PROPERTY IS ON A 60 DAY NOTICE.
THEY ARE LOCATED NEAR HWY 620 IN NORTHWEST AUSTIN.
THE COMMUNITY WAS BUILT IN 2001 LOCATED IN WILLIAMSON COUNTY.
Matt Davidson ~~Over 28 years of leasing experience in Austin~~
